values:
Fun as hell. Kinda wish I was still there...

End of story.


I'm bored and I thought I should post something...

So...I just got yelled at because I had a "tone" that made my dad feel stupid and like a jerk. Oh, he went off on me; trying to make me feel the same way apparently. Even said "fuck". Whoa jeez! :-P 

He should feel stupid because that's what I think of him and my mum half that time. Stupid...very stupid and selfish.

Can't wait til I'm off to college...hopefully away from home.

So...I love it when my Dad or Mum lie through their teeth when they talk to my counselor.  

And I love how I sit there and choke on all the things I wanna spit out at 'em.

So today was the best I've had in a VERY long time. I miss my threesomes with my two best friends, along with Noonan....so I guess it's really a foursome...

I was told to post something....because I've apparently had a LJ for a good while now and I totally forgot about it. So yeah...

This should also be good for my mental health, hah...some of you know, or should know, what I'm talkin' about. If not, well, if I keep up with this...thing, you may find out.
